96
00:14:46,616 --> 00:14:50,016
井の中の蛙 大会優勝者 未練たらたら エステ
The frog in the well, the tournament winner, lingering with regrets... EST

97
00:14:50,116 --> 00:14:54,516
熱中自尊心なんて到底ないな
I have absolutely no obsessive self-esteem

98
00:14:54,616 --> 00:14:58,416
愛を歌っては愛されたことない 未体験回答
Singing of love, yet never loved; an inexperienced response

99
00:14:58,516 --> 00:15:02,316
毎度退場障害 耐え難い 正反対でいたい
Exit obstacles every time, it's unbearable; I want to be the exact opposite

100
00:15:05,024 --> 00:15:08,224
別に不満などないけれど
I have no particular complaints,

101
00:15:08,224 --> 00:15:11,624
描いた夢と違うけれど
though it's different from the dream I drew.

102
00:15:11,624 --> 00:15:15,524
なぜか心に穴が空いたようだ
For some reason, it's as if there's a hole in my heart.

103
00:15:15,524 --> 00:15:18,324
気づいてしまうから
Because I realize it,

104
00:15:19,624 --> 00:15:23,024
