To this ordinary life,

105
00:15:23,424 --> 00:15:26,024
今ピリオドを打て
put a period to it now.

106
00:15:26,024 --> 00:15:28,724
混ざり合うようなこの気持ちが
This feeling that seems to blend together,

107
00:15:28,724 --> 00:15:30,824
抑えようもない衝動が
this uncontrollable impulse,

108
00:15:30,824 --> 00:15:35,324
望み通り叶わない現実になって
it becomes a reality that doesn't go as hoped,

109
00:15:35,324 --> 00:15:37,424
まだまだくたばってなんかないぜ
but I'm not dead and gone just yet.

110
00:15:37,424 --> 00:15:39,524
神に誓ってないと想え
Know that I haven't sworn to any god,

111
00:15:39,524 --> 00:15:41,524
