looking at the end of a formless future.

112
00:15:41,524 --> 00:15:45,524
騒ぐ心の内を聞こう
Let's listen to the noise within our hearts,

113
00:15:45,524 --> 00:15:49,324
夢の狭間で廃れぬよう
so we don't fade away between dreams.

114
00:15:49,324 --> 00:15:53,324
足を止めていられぬよう
So that we cannot stop in our tracks,

115
00:15:53,324 --> 00:15:57,524
コロロン 甘い声放（ほう）
Kororon, let out a sweet voice.

116
00:16:05,024 --> 00:16:08,524
言葉では何とでも言える 此処が正念場
You can say anything with words; this is the climax.

117
00:16:08,524 --> 00:16:12,524
そう 野外は愛のないディスカッション アテにやっていけ
Yeah, handle the loveless outdoor discussions.

118
00:16:12,524 --> 00:16:15,524
その結果が全てなんだ 嬉し難いが
That result is everything, though it's bittersweet.

119
00:16:15,524 --> 00:16:19,524
千載一遇だ まだ生かしてくれよ 世界の中
It's a once-in-a-lifetime chance; let me live on.

120
00:16:19,524 --> 00:16:23,524
定かではないが まだ僕の中には
I'm not sure, but inside me still remains

121
00:16:23,524 --> 00:16:28,024
数多余す事のない事実が
countless undeniable facts.

122
00:16:28,024 --> 00:16:31,524
泥に飼い慣らされるこの毎日が
These days of being tamed by the mud...

123
00:16:31,524 --> 00:16:35,024
嫌 食べられてしまい
No, I'll end up being devoured.

124
00:16:51,524 --> 00:16:54,524
実は不安しかないけれど
Actually, I'm filled with nothing but anxiety,

125
00:16:54,524 --> 00:16:59,024
描いた夢もないけれど
and I have no dreams either.

126
00:16:59,024 --> 00:17:03,524
だから心に穴が空いたようだ
That's why it feels like there's a hole in my heart.

127
00:17:03,524 --> 00:17:06,524
気づいてしまった
I've realized it now.

128
00:17:06,524 --> 00:17:13,024
ありきたりな人生に 今ピリオドを打て
Put a period to this ordinary life now.

129
00:17:15,524 --> 00:17:18,224
混ざり合うようなこの気持ちが
This feeling that seems to blend together,

130
00:17:18,224 --> 00:17:20,324
抑えようもない衝動が
this uncontrollable impulse,

131
00:17:20,324 --> 00:17:24,824
望み通り叶わない現実になって
it becomes a reality that doesn't go as hoped,

132
00:17:24,824 --> 00:17:26,924
まだまだくたばってなんかないぜ
but I'm not dead and gone just yet.

133
00:17:26,924 --> 00:17:29,024
神に誓ってないと想え
Know that I haven't sworn to any god,

134
00:17:29,024 --> 00:17:31,024
実体のない将来に果て見て
looking at the end of a formless future.

135
00:17:32,024 --> 00:17:36,024
騒ぐ心の内を聞こう
Let's listen to the noise within our hearts,

136
00:17:36,024 --> 00:17:40,024
夢の狭間で廃れぬよう
so we don't fade away between dreams.

137
00:17:40,024 --> 00:17:44,024
足を止めていられぬよう
So that we cannot stop in our tracks,

138
00:17:44,024 --> 00:17:48,024
コロロン 甘い声放（ほう）
Kororon, let out a sweet voice.

139
00:18:09,024 --> 00:18:14,524
Yay! Woo!

140
00:18:15,024 --> 00:18:20,524
Thank you so much for coming everyone to my 3D live.

141
00:18:20,524 --> 00:18:23,024
My name is Ouro Kronii from Hololive English,

142
00:18:23,024 --> 00:18:27,024
and we have Sora-senpai!

143
00:18:27,024 --> 00:18:33,024
こんそらめー！ Hello! I'm Tokino Sora!
Kon-sora-me! Hello! I'm Tokino Sora!

144
00:18:33,524 --> 00:18:36,024
Kronii, Happy Birthday!

145
00:18:36,024 --> 00:18:38,024
Thank you!

146
00:18:38,024 --> 00:18:40,024
Very gorgeous outfit!

147
00:18:40,024 --> 00:18:43,024
ありがとうございます！
Thank you so much!

148
00:18:43,024 --> 00:18:45,024
Thank you!

149
00:18:45,024 --> 00:18:49,024
Oh man, look at the stage here.

150
00:18:49,024 --> 00:18:51,524
Very beautiful.

151
00:18:51,524 --> 00:18:54,024
Ah, so pretty! Look at the night sky!

152
00:18:54,024 --> 00:18:57,024
綺麗！ Wow...
Beautiful! Wow...

153
00:18:57,024 --> 00:19:00,024
Oh man...

154
00:19:00,024 --> 00:19:05,524
Oh, Kronii, Kronii. Why did you invite me

155
00:19:05,524 --> 00:19:08,024
to your birthday live?

156
00:19:08,024 --> 00:19:13,024
Oh, uh, well, last year, we hung out together

157
00:19:13,024 --> 00:19:16,524
a bit and I had a lot of fun.

158
00:19:16,524 --> 00:19:21,024
So I wanted to invite you

159
00:19:21,024 --> 00:19:25,024
and get to sing together.

160
00:19:25,024 --> 00:19:29,024
I thought that would have been really great,

161
00:19:29,024 --> 00:19:32,024
so thank you for coming!

162
00:19:32,024 --> 00:19:33,524
Thank you! Yay!

163
00:19:33,524 --> 00:19:36,024
I... so I love you!

164
00:19:36,024 --> 00:19:40,024
Oh my god! Love is such a strong word...

165
00:19:40,024 --> 00:19:43,024
I, I love you too.

166
00:19:43,024 --> 00:19:47,524
I want to go to... uh, udon eating with you!
I want to go to... udon eating with you!

167
00:19:47,524 --> 00:19:50,024
Oh, udon!

168
00:19:50,024 --> 00:19:51,024
Yeah!

169
00:19:51,024 --> 00:19:55,024
Yeah! Let's go eat! Oh my god!

170
00:19:55,024 --> 00:19:58,024
We'll get anything! What kind of udon?

171
00:19:58,024 --> 00:20:02,024
I like anything!

172
00:20:02,024 --> 00:20:05,024
Me too!

173
00:20:03,972 --> 00:20:05,372
Anything? Yeah, I like anything.

174
00:20:05,972 --> 00:20:07,572
あ、他には？
Ah, anything else?

175
00:20:07,972 --> 00:20:09,372
Ah, you know, there's like cold udon

176
00:20:09,372 --> 00:20:11,872
and then there's just like udon with like soup

177
00:20:11,872 --> 00:20:14,872
and then there's like onsen tamago and all that.

178
00:20:15,172 --> 00:20:16,872
